history.content:
Ever needed a little extra push to start your own side project?

Create a personal website or build a startup! Cal Hacks is proud to present Hack Month, a brand-new initiative for college students to meet other passionate innovators and motivate one another to build their own projects from the ground up. Open to all university students, all majors, all ideas. 💡

📆 Application are due TOMORROW, September 18th @ 11:59pm PDT

🌟 Sign up today: links.calhacks.io/hackmonth_application

💻 Learn more: https://hackmonth.calhacks.io
